amily: 宋体;font-size: 14.0pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 4.（3分）D&nbsp;&nbsp; 略：平定。</span></p><p align="left">    <span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14.0pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 5.（3分）D&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;①④非太祖所为，②与题目无关。故为③⑤⑥。</span></p><p align="left">    <span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14.0pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 6.（3分）C&nbsp;&nbsp; 张无忌将《武穆遗书》传给徐达，而不是太祖，故C误。</span></p><p align="left">    <span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14.0pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 7.（10分）（略）</span></p><p align="left">    <span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14.0pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;（二）（11分）</span></p><p align="left">    <span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14.0pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;8.（5分）</span></p><p align="left">    <span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14.0pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14.0pt;">可参考原文：《侠客行》第二十章：侠客行。</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14.0pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p align="left">    <span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14.0pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;9.（6分）</span></p><p align="left">    <span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14.0pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14.0pt;">可参考原文：《侠客行》第二十章：侠客行。</span></p><p align="left">    <span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14.0pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;（三）（6分）</span></p><p align="left">    <span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14.0pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;10.（6分）（1）<span style="font-family: 楷体_GB2312;">双眸粲粲如星&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;塞上牛羊空许约</span></span></p><p align="left">    <span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14.0pt;"><span style="font-family: 楷体_GB2312;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style="font-family: 宋体;">见《天龙八部》第二十一章至第二十五章</span></span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14.0pt;">章节名称。</span></p><p align="left">    <span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14.0pt;"